%F A172073 a(n) = Sum_{i=0..n} A051866(i). (End)
%F A172073 a(n) = 4*a(n-1) - 6*a(n-2) + 4*a(n-3) - a(n-4) for n > 3, a(0)=0, a(1)=1, a(2)=15, a(3)=54. - _Harvey P. Dale_, Jan 29 2013
%F A172073 a(n) = Sum_{i=0..n-1} (n-i)*(12*i+1), with a(0)=0. - _Bruno Berselli_, Feb 10 2014
