%F A172073 Sum_{n>=1} 1/a(n) = 4*Pi/21 + 8*log(2)/7 - 2/7.
%F A172073 Sum_{n>=1} (-1)^(n+1)/a(n) = 4*sqrt(2)*Pi/21 + 8*sqrt(2)*log(sqrt(2)+2)/21 - (20 + 4*sqrt(2))*log(2)/21 + 2/7. (End)
%F A172073 E.g.f.: exp(x)*x*(2 + 13*x + 4*x^2)/2. - _Elmo R. Oliveira_, Aug 04 2025
